      {
        "type": "email",
        "html": "<p>Hello {first_name, \"there\"},</p><p>August is here, but not quite the summer holidays for me yet. I still have a mix of marking, training and writing to do. I hope to be in “vacation mode” sometime next week. And that might, ironically, lead to a small uptick in posting here…</p><p>One thing I am doing, though, is <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/2021/08/twitter-social-distancing/\">taking a step back from Twitter</a>, for reasons I did my best to articulate earlier. I'd be <em>really</em> interested in hearing from any of you who have stepped back from Twitter or struggled with your time there — or, conversely, if you're finding it incredibly valuable.</p>"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Subscriptions. Subscriptions everywhere. ",
